{"tid":697120,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"嚇到小孩退散！伊藤潤二「人頭氣球」真實出現","createTime":"2018-06-10T16:36:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-11T02:53:28.000Z","uid":37554,"like":81,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"d199eba9dcf7e49f1923d593ca1f711feed62e25","tid":697120,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T16:36:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180610/640_7042d373a97fb791f063870e90b6ab6c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180610%2F640_7042d373a97fb791f063870e90b6ab6c.jpg&h=152ed658&s={SIZE}\" />許多家長會帶小孩去公園放風箏，但如果抬頭看到這一幕，恐怕小孩會想回家了吧！一名網友今天在臉書社團「爆廢公社」轉po一張照片，天空中一個巨大的氣球，竟然是一顆恐怖的人頭造型，網友們看了直呼太嚇人，又紛紛表示想買。<br />\n<br />\n日本網友也分享了這張照片，並立即將它與恐怖漫畫大師伊藤潤二的《人頭氣球》做連結，覺得根本重現場景。而台灣有網友則表示，這應該是伊藤潤二鬼屋活動的氣球。<br />\n<br />\n其他網友則紛紛留言「Fuck也太恐怖」、「小孩子都被嚇跑了」、「這厲害了他媽的」、「七月半熱賣商品」、「好想要」、「進擊的富江」、「請原諒我，我第一眼看到，只有靠而已」、「WTF，以後看天空都有陰影」。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180610/640_262dec4f5e793b4bc7a4bfefe3c9bc0c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180610%2F640_262dec4f5e793b4bc7a4bfefe3c9bc0c.jpg&h=1c539bf4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b271fc19d3c7c436c46e49ce2172f15163d80fbd","tid":697120,"uid":89681,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T16:37:55.000Z","msg":"cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7a266b0e44a0b2a24e27e9ec03e634a404e7585","tid":697120,"uid":13474,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T16:38:58.000Z","msg":"夜晚見到真心驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fd816b1867691ade586a009ea9897fd0e4fa6a4","tid":697120,"uid":6192,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,